  "content": "<ul>\n<li>Certaines aptitudes et certains dangers environnementaux, comme la faim et les effets &agrave; long terme des temp&eacute;ratures glaciales et &eacute;touffantes, provoquent un &eacute;tat particulier appel&eacute; l'&eacute;puisement. Celui-ci se divise en six niveaux. Un effet peut donner un ou plusieurs niveaux d'&eacute;puisement, comme indiqu&eacute; dans la description de chaque effet.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"table-container\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-x: auto; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<table style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2rem;\">\n<thead style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 'Spectral SC', serif; background-color: #b5aab9; color: #ffffff;\">\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">\n<th style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 6px 12px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; border-bottom: none !important;\">Niveau</th>\n<th style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 6px 12px; margin: 0px; text-align: left; border-bottom: none !important;\">Effet</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 6px 12px; margin: 0px; border-bottom: none !important; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">1</span></td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 6px 12px; margin: 0px; border-bottom: none !important;\"><a class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; color: var(--v-anchor-base);\" href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#avantage-et-desavantage\"><em style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">d&eacute;savantage</em></a>&nbsp;lors des&nbsp;<a class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; color: var(--v-anchor-base);\" href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#tests-de-caracteristique\">tests de caract&eacute;ristique</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-color: #ededed;\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 6px 12px; margin: 0px; border-bottom: none !important; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">2</span></td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 6px 12px; margin: 0px; border-bottom: none !important;\">Vitesse r&eacute;duite de moiti&eacute;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 6px 12px; margin: 0px; border-bottom: none !important; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">3</span></td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 6px 12px; margin: 0px; border-bottom: none !important;\"><a class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; color: var(--v-anchor-base);\" href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#avantage-et-desavantage\"><em style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">d&eacute;savantage</em></a>&nbsp;lors des attaques et des sauvegardes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-color: #ededed;\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 6px 12px; margin: 0px; border-bottom: none !important; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">4</span></td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 6px 12px; margin: 0px; border-bottom: none !important;\">Maximum de points de vie r&eacute;duit de moiti&eacute;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 6px 12px; margin: 0px; border-bottom: none !important; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">5</span></td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 6px 12px; margin: 0px; border-bottom: none !important;\">Vitesse r&eacute;duite &agrave; 0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-color: #ededed;\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 6px 12px; margin: 0px; border-bottom: none !important; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">6</span></td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 6px 12px; margin: 0px; border-bottom: none !important;\">D&eacute;c&egrave;s</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<ul>\n<li>Si une cr&eacute;ature d&eacute;j&agrave; &eacute;puis&eacute;e souffre d'un nouvel effet g&eacute;n&eacute;rant de l'&eacute;puisement, son niveau d'&eacute;puisement actuel augmente du montant indiqu&eacute; dans la description de l'effet.</li>\n<li>Une cr&eacute;ature souffre des effets de son niveau d'&eacute;puisement actuel et de tous les effets des niveaux inf&eacute;rieurs. Par exemple, une cr&eacute;ature afflig&eacute;e d'un &eacute;puisement de niveau 2 voit sa vitesse r&eacute;duite de moiti&eacute; et subit un&nbsp;<a class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: var(--v-anchor-base);\" href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#avantage-et-desavantage\"><em style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">d&eacute;savantage</em></a>&nbsp;lors de ses&nbsp;<a class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: var(--v-anchor-base);\" href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/utiliser-les-caracteristiques/#tests-de-caracteristique\">tests de caract&eacute;ristique</a>.</li>\n<li>Un effet qui r&eacute;duit l'&eacute;puisement diminue son niveau du montant indiqu&eacute; dans sa description. Tous les effets d'&eacute;puisement se terminent si le niveau d'&eacute;puisement de la cr&eacute;ature est r&eacute;duit &agrave; moins de 1.</li>\n<li>Une fois termin&eacute;, un repos long r&eacute;duit le niveau d'&eacute;puisement d'une cr&eacute;ature de 1, &agrave; condition qu'elle ait eu &agrave; boire et &agrave; manger.</li>\n</ul>",
